1. Get yourself a ruby environment, chruby with ruby-build isn't bad

2. `apt-get install build-essential openssl libreadline6 libreadline6-dev curl git zlib1g zlib1g-dev libssl-dev libyaml-dev libsqlite3-dev sqlite3 libxml2-dev libxslt-dev autoconf libc6-dev ncurses-dev automake libtool bison subversion pkg-config`

3. `gem install jekyll`

4. `gem install therubyracer  # Javascript engine`

5. `gem install rdiscount  # Markdown parser`

6. `rbenv rehash`
